title: Business Opening Hours Pro Plugin - Premium WordPress Plugins
description:
Business Opening Hours Pro Plugin gives out the easiest ways to manage all your business opening hours including office timings, shop hours and store hours. The richly featured Business Opening Hours Pro performs well with various websites which are much concerned about maintaining time discipline. Contains external links.

To install:
1. Upload the folder to the /wp-content/plugins/ directory
2. Activate the plugin through the 'Plugins' menu in WordPress
